  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/592380/extras/0cf6468c2680a884c8862e895fa9da65.avif?t=1667921767\" width=617 height=317 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/592380/extras/f0f70b94214846009ce80e0bd8c7747d.poster.avif?t=1667921767\" width=608 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/592380/extras/f0f70b94214846009ce80e0bd8c7747d.webm?t=1667921767\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/592380/extras/f0f70b94214846009ce80e0bd8c7747d.mp4?t=1667921767\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Adventure Story + Arcade Action = Awesomeness</h2>Apocalypse Cow is like a Pixar movie... if it was directed by Tarantino as a violent and explosive arcade adventure! Fight thugs, strippers, insecure robots and Netflix watching wizards. Rupture time to slow down traps, outrun bullets or blow up boxes and freeze them mid-air to jump on them! Destroy your enemies, solve puzzles, follow the story and get lost in a digital world full of peculiar characters.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/592380/extras/45155a5bf21d1d1bf2ec77349f45d7f0.poster.avif?t=1667921767\" width=200 height=26 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/592380/extras/45155a5bf21d1d1bf2ec77349f45d7f0.webm?t=1667921767\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Play locally with a friend  - levels change to present challenges designed for two!</li><li>Unlock the COOLEST pop-culture costumes EVER!</li><li>Unleash hell with Katanas, Bazookas or exotic options like the Shrinker or Mjolnir!</li><li>Two Game modes: Default (hardcore) and Granny Mode (for those with finger arthritis)</li><li>Unlockable Speedrunner Mode (compete against the level designer's time!)</li><li>Challenging, level-specific achievements that ask you to change the way you play.</li><li>Full speech! Wow!</li><li>Nice graphics and stuff.</li></ul><br>Add <strong>Apocalypse Cow</strong> to your Wishlist to be notified when it launches!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/592380/extras/7cf94949c541426009005915b43095e7.poster.avif?t=1667921767\" width=612 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/592380/extras/7cf94949c541426009005915b43095e7.webm?t=1667921767\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/592380/extras/7cf94949c541426009005915b43095e7.mp4?t=1667921767\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/592380/extras/0cf6468c2680a884c8862e895fa9da65.avif?t=1667921767\" width=617 height=317 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/592380/extras/f0f70b94214846009ce80e0bd8c7747d.poster.avif?t=1667921767\" width=608 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/592380/extras/f0f70b94214846009ce80e0bd8c7747d.webm?t=1667921767\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/592380/extras/f0f70b94214846009ce80e0bd8c7747d.mp4?t=1667921767\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Adventure Story + Arcade Action = Awesomeness</h2>Apocalypse Cow is like a Pixar movie... if it was directed by Tarantino as a violent and explosive arcade adventure! Fight thugs, strippers, insecure robots and Netflix watching wizards. Rupture time to slow down traps, outrun bullets or blow up boxes and freeze them mid-air to jump on them! Destroy your enemies, solve puzzles, follow the story and get lost in a digital world full of peculiar characters.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/592380/extras/45155a5bf21d1d1bf2ec77349f45d7f0.poster.avif?t=1667921767\" width=200 height=26 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/592380/extras/45155a5bf21d1d1bf2ec77349f45d7f0.webm?t=1667921767\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Play locally with a friend  - levels change to present challenges designed for two!</li><li>Unlock the COOLEST pop-culture costumes EVER!</li><li>Unleash hell with Katanas, Bazookas or exotic options like the Shrinker or Mjolnir!</li><li>Two Game modes: Default (hardcore) and Granny Mode (for those with finger arthritis)</li><li>Unlockable Speedrunner Mode (compete against the level designer's time!)</li><li>Challenging, level-specific achievements that ask you to change the way you play.</li><li>Full speech! Wow!</li><li>Nice graphics and stuff.</li></ul><br>Add <strong>Apocalypse Cow</strong> to your Wishlist to be notified when it launches!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/592380/extras/7cf94949c541426009005915b43095e7.poster.avif?t=1667921767\" width=612 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/592380/extras/7cf94949c541426009005915b43095e7.webm?t=1667921767\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/592380/extras/7cf94949c541426009005915b43095e7.mp4?t=1667921767\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
